sub_title: Urban designer and planner at Royal HaskoningDHV
summary: I am a Colombian urban designer, living and working in the Netherlands. I have experience in the urban development sector both in Colombia and the Netherlands. I have worked in various cities on strategic urban design and participation projects, together with clients, residents, entrepreneurs, and other parties. I am a curious and ambitious professional with an interest in sustainability in cities and integrated urban development. Always ready to roll up my sleeves to come up with solutions that have a real impact.
